	<item>
		<title>The eNaira struggled as a wallet. Now the CBN wants it to power payments.</title>
		<link>https://techcabal.com/2026/06/09/cbns-vision-2028-gives-the-enaira-a-second-lifeline/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Frank Eleanya]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 13:42:30 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Analysis]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[cbdc]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[CBN]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[eNaira]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Nigeria]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Payment System]]></category>
